# Wickham Market District Ward

Wickham Market District Ward is a district ward in East Suffolk district, in Suffolk, England. From 2023 it has consisted of the following nine wards:
* Campsea Ash
* Farnham
* Hacheston
* Little Glemham
* Marlesford
* Pettistree
* Stratford St Andrew
* Wickham Market
* Ufford
